{
  "id": "crate-secretsx-ijol",
  "title": "Tier-2 and regional cloud secrets manager backends",
  "description": "Implement secretx backends for cloud providers beyond AWS/Azure/GCP: OCI Vault, IBM Cloud SM, Alibaba Cloud SM, Tencent SSM, Huawei CSMS, Yandex Lockbox, OpenStack Barbican, and Scaleway SM. Each has a stub README in its crate directory documenting the planned URI format and auth model. Implements the 'also-ran' global clouds plus European OpenStack-based providers and Chinese clouds. All 8 are read/write (WritableSecretStore); OCI Vault also supports SigningBackend.",
